More correctly the caption should read &quot;Locomotive 5712 a member of the D57-class, 1954&quot; 

From the 1924 classification the first two numerals denoted the class (ie 57 class) the last two the member of that class (ie this is the twelfth locomotive of the 57 class) and the prefix &quot;D&quot; denoted 4 driving axles
